      <p class="text-dark-300 mb-4">
        If you are using Skillsmith on behalf of an organization, you represent and warrant that you
        have the authority to bind that organization to these Terms, and "you" refers to both you
        individually and that organization.
      </p>
      <p class="text-dark-300">
        We may modify these Terms at any time. Material changes will be communicated via email or
        through the service. Your continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of the modified Terms.
      </p>
