        <li><strong class="text-white">API Access:</strong> Programmatic access to skill discovery and management</li>
        <li><strong class="text-white">MCP Integration:</strong> Native integration with Claude Code via Model Context Protocol</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-dark-300">
        We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the service at any time,
        with or without notice. We will make reasonable efforts to notify users of significant changes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: User Accounts -->
