      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">3. User Accounts</h2>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Account Creation</h3>
      <p class="text-dark-300 mb-4">
        Some features of Skillsmith require an account. When creating an account, you must:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-dark-300 space-y-2 ml-4 mb-6">
        <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
        <li>Be at least 13 years old (or 16 in the EEA)</li>
        <li>Not create accounts for others without permission</li>
        <li>Not use automated methods to create accounts</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Account Security</h3>
      <p class="text-dark-300 mb-4">You are responsible for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-dark-300 space-y-2 ml-4 mb-6">
        <li>Maintaining the confidentiality of your credentials</li>
        <li>All activities that occur under your account</li>
        <li>Notifying us immediately of any unauthorized access</li>
        <li>Keeping your API keys secure and rotating them if compromised</li>
