          <h4 class="font-semibold text-yellow-400 mb-2">Automated Access</h4>
          <p class="text-dark-300 text-sm">
            Automated access is permitted only through our official API with valid authentication.
            Automated scraping of the website is prohibited. Rate limits apply to all automated access.
